sources.title: The Journey Is The Destination | Full Movie | Action Drama | The True | Ella Purnell
sources.description:
THE JOURNEY IS THE DESTINATION is based on the remarkable true story of the life of Dan Eldon (Ben Schnetzer), a photographer, artist, and adventurer.  By the age of 22, he had traveled to more than 40 countries, created fine art journals, worked with refugees, been hired as the youngest photojournalist at Reuters, fallen in love  â€” and accumulated more life experience than most in a lifetime.  Witty and inspiring, the film tells the story of a young man coming of age to realize his purpose, and his belief that we can all create positive change.
2016.  Stars: Ben Schnetzer, Kelly Macdonald, Sam Hazeldine, Ella Purnell

metadata.Plot: While watching a car race at McKinley Speedway, Nick O'Bannon has a premonition of a car crash that will result in many casualties, including several people that are in the audience. Nick convinces his girlfriend Lori, along with his friends Hunt and Janet to leave. A security guard named George Lanter, along with a racist named Carter, a mother and her two sons, and several other people follow Nick out. Shortly after they leave, Nick's premonition comes true. When survivors start dying, Nick, his friends, and George must try to find the remaining survivors and save them from Death before it is too late.
metadata.Actors: Nick Zano, Krista Allen, Andrew Fiscella
